<p>Note from the author</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Thank you very much to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/almarduk" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3672751); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3672751&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564673618" alt="Almarduk" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3672751)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/almarduk" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3672751); return false;">Almarduk</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agente-marw" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1874588); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1874588&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564673618" alt="Agente marw" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1874588)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agente-marw" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1874588); return false;">Agente marw</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564673618" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;">Uncle Nicolini</a></span> and <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/revenantheimdall" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2352752); return false;">RevenantHeimdall</a></span> for their feedback.</p>
<p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564673618" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;">Uncle Nicolini</a></span> for translating this to English.</p>
<p>Also, thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564673618" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;">DarkStuff</a></span> for creating one of my favourite GoIs and to you, dear reader.</p>
<p>This' my first GoI Format and the first GoI Format of the first canon of the ES-Branch (too many first, huh?) and introduces Wilson to the canon and Latinamerica.</p>
<p>I know I'm not an expert writer, so I'm open to feedback!</p>
<p>Again, thank you very much for reading and hope you like it! :D<br />
