<p>Wilson Wildlife Solutions is a paranormal wildlife project funded by the Foundation and based in the United States, Japan, and Latin America. Although initially a state project and known to exist since 1999, it was not until the Megaptera Incident in 2001 that its existence was officially recognized and a relationship established between the two groups. Currently, the Boring Agreement describes that Wilson Wildlife Solutions must be supervised by DMs specializing in wildlife in the Regions in which it operates, and that they can handle anomalies based on wildlife containment that are either Safe or Euclid with varying degrees of Foundation intervention (on a case-by-case basis). Amendments to the Boring Agreement can be, and have been, made to take into account grey areas or new policies as necessary.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>In the canon they are much more expanded than usual, and The Foundation has much more confidence in them. They have a very good image in the anomalous world and Tim Wilson is considered by some to be an anomalous 'celebrity'.</p>
</blockquote>
